{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Life on a knife's edge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The blood on your hands was not worth it, but you can't change that now. Explore Gravdal, a small town with a bad reputation, nested in the shadow of great mountains and rolling hills. Plot with wicked syndicates and grab whatever money you can to fund your escape.\u00a0It's\u00a0only\u00a0a\u00a0matter of\u00a0time\u00a0before\u00a0the\u00a0law,\u00a0or\u00a0your mind, catches\u00a0up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283090/extras/description_header_2.png?t=1736352539\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Your own worst enemy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you're not hiding from police or flashing guns at cashiers; take a moment for self-care. Eat something, take a shower or pop some pills. For when nightmares come alive, preparedness may be the difference between waking up in a cold sweat \u2014 or not waking up at all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283090/extras/description_header_3_w_fade.png?t=1736352539\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reactive sanity system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gib-rich combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A mix of linear and open levels with secrets to discover</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlockable game mode and weapons</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283090/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736352539","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283090/page.bg.jpg?t=1736352539","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283090/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736352539","capsule_imagev5":"htt